    - target: {fileID: 2636065031202590820, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: Consort Yu took her own life as her Lovers army fell. Where she was
        burried, red poppies grew. Perishing for love.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
