    - target: {fileID: 5109087311396199045, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: plantData
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8b80860e365a1f148977707a26a0d4c5, type: 2}
    - target: {fileID: 5109087311396199045, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: scatterer
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 3137393489738898555}
    - target: {fileID: 5109087311396199045, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: selectionCollider
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 7360644032639454882}
    - target: {fileID: 5122842465899161861, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "The Poppy\n\nSummer set lip to earth's bosom bare, \nAnd left the flush'd
        print in a poppy there; \nLike a yawn of fire from the grass it came, \nAnd
        the fanning wind puff'd it to flapping flame. \nWith burnt mouth red like
        a lion's it drank \nThe blood of the sun as he slaughter'd sank, \nAnd dipp'd
        its cup in the purpurate shine \nWhen the eastern conduits ran with wine.
        \nTill it grew lethargied with fierce bliss \n,And hot as a swinked gipsy
        is, \nAnd drowsed in sleepy savageries, \nWith mouth wide a-pout for a sultry
        kiss.\n\n\u2014 Francis Thompson"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5122842465899161861, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_TextStyleHashCode
      value: -1183493901
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5431834928911583797, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f7a59ffc02c800b4790afaafd4a7fc55, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 5488519469664222319, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "Song of Consort Yu:\n\n\u6F22\u5175\u5DF2\u7565\u5730\uFF0C\n\u56DB\u9762\u695A\u6B4C\u8072\u3002\n\u5927\u738B\u7FA9\u6C23\u76E1\uFF0C\n\u8CE4\u59BE\u4F55\u804A\u751F\u3002\n\nHan
        forces have conquered our land;\nSurrounded by Chu songs;\nMy King's spirits
        are low;\nWhy then should I live?"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5902464882853280731, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: instanceId
      value: 8dfb1337-e198-48d4-8dfd-4ad3e84660f2
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5956918439778082410, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "In China, the common Poppy is known as y\xFAm\u011Bir\xE9n, \"Yu the
        Beauty\"."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5956918439778082416, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: You fold a petal into a little pouch, bring your hands together with
        a smack, and the louder it bursts, the more your love is said to love you
        back.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6181259333930047258, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: GsplatAsset
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 4599839170941234424, guid: 3d8cb0da1ebb9f841bda7de6712ee6fd, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 6181259333930047258, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_assetGuid
      value: 3d8cb0da1ebb9f841bda7de6712ee6fd
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6835627233580907840, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 82b7596615658b04bbb505be5febd703, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 7173199714940506848, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: Poppies grow in the midst of the summer, red, hot, and they often don't
        keep.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7173199714940506848, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_TextStyleHashCode
      value: -1183493901
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7417057368276200879, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1065fb59b2145704ba5f45a9e2217a98, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 8582845393027873350, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_IsActive
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8810918796485297829, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 451df8256d5775d409b0d71b94ede592, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 9161542878112791018, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: It's german name is Klatschmohn, literally "clapping poppy". This Comes
        from an old game About love.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 9161542878112791018, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_TextStyleHashCode
      value: -1183493901
